overview: This 3-DVD collection is the most comprehensive ever assembled on the Saturn V. Packed with spectacular footage, from every launch of a Saturn V to unique management reports, an original documentary, pad camera footage and more. Rare extras of engine tests, rollouts, pad operations. One of most popular sets ever.
tagline: This DVD set is an excellent documentary outlining the history and development of this incredible machine - the Saturn V
title: The Mighty Saturns: Saturn V
